  sleep questionnaire application. The agent systematically navigated through
  the application, testing the questionnaire flow, form validation, report
  generation, and admin login. It confirmed that core functionalities like
  section navigation, conditional fields, PDF generation, and API endpoints were
  working correctly. The agent also identified minor issues, including ESLint
  warnings and an outdated page title. Following the testing, the agent provided
  a detailed summary of its findings and recommendations. Subsequently, it
  proceeded to implement the suggested fixes, specifically updating the page
  title and committing various feature enhancements (schema updates, new form
  sections, report improvements, PDF generation updates, CSV export, and form
  functionality) in a series of atomic, conventionally-formatted Git commits.
